@startuml
autonumber
box "Orchestration Layer" #LightCyan
participant "Camunda Engine" as Camunda
participant "Kong Gateway" as Kong
end box
box "Microservice Layer" #LightYellow
participant "Grid Balancing MS" as GBMS
participant "Telemetry MS" as TMS
participant "UtilityOperator MS" as UOMS
end box
box "Messaging Layer" #Thistle
queue "Kafka Topic:\nGridBalancingRecommendation" as Kafka
end box
box "Persistence Layer" #LightGreen
database "AWS RDS\n(GridBalancing DB)" as DB
end box

== Grid Balancing Recommendation ==

Camunda -> Kong: Trigger Grid Balancing Evaluation
Kong -> GBMS: POST /evaluate
GBMS -> Kong: GET /telemetry/zone/{zoneId}/aggregated
Kong -> TMS: Forward GET /telemetry/zone/{zoneId}/aggregated
TMS --> Kong: 200 OK {totalLoad_kw, avgSoC_percent}
Kong --> GBMS: 200 OK {totalLoad_kw, avgSoC_percent}
GBMS -> GBMS: Compare totalLoad_kw\nagainst zone maxLoad_kw
note right: If totalLoad_kw > maxLoad_kw\n-> Zone exceeds safety threshold\n-> Scan neighbouring zones for surplus
GBMS -> Kong: GET /telemetry/zone/{neighbourZoneId}/aggregated
Kong -> TMS: Forward GET /telemetry/zone/{neighbourZoneId}/aggregated
TMS --> Kong: 200 OK {totalLoad_kw, avgSoC_percent}
Kong --> GBMS: 200 OK {totalLoad_kw, avgSoC_percent}
GBMS -> GBMS: Identify surplus zone\nand recommended action
GBMS -> DB: JDBC INSERT grid_balancing_recommendation\n(id, stressedZoneId, surplusZoneId,\nrecommendedAction, timestamp)
DB --> GBMS: 200 OK
GBMS -> Kafka: Publish GridBalancingRecommendation\n{recommendationId, stressedZoneId,\nsurplusZoneId, recommendedAction, timestamp}
Kafka --> GBMS: Ack
GBMS --> Kong: 200 OK {recommendationId}
Kong --> Camunda: Evaluation Complete

loop continuous polling
    UOMS -> Kafka: consume from \nGridBalancingRecommendation
    Kafka --> UOMS: JSON Payload
end
@enduml